/ id    type    color
/ #     wall    black
/ .     ground  white
/ 1..F  shelf   brown (initial stock)
/ 0     shelf   brown (full: 16)
/ _     station reddish-pink
/ v     dropoff cyan
/ ~     null    n/a
/ shelf stock is encoded directly in one hex character

/ cinematic layout: long runway corridor with side depots for sweeping pan shots and speed emphasis
/ best for recording: central lane keeps robot motion readable while side shelves add depth

